---
title: Seared Mexican Chicken Tacos with Creamy Slaw, Smashed Avo & Coriander
description: A juicy, flavourful chicken steak is one of our favourite taco fillings, especially paired with a variety of bright accompaniments. A
creamy radish slaw and mellow smashed avo fulfill those requirements perfectly is this crowd-pleasing dish. Throw it all in a warm tortilla and you’re good to go!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6688a35ddea0224ab0733551-50c1f1e9.jpeg
